imentalists to confirm the exotic dynamical magnetic properties\nunveiled here, with a rich mixture of acoustic and optical features.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Jun 2020 20:17:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 16 Sep 2020 15:44:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-17"}
