id progress\nin localizing FRBs will further tighten the constraints on both $m_{\\gamma}$\nand $\\rm DM_{host}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Jun 2020 06:44:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 18 Jun 2020 02:46:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-13"}
